---
import SectionOrnament from "./SectionOrnament.astro";
---
<section class="features position-relative" id="features" aria-labelledby="features-title">
  <div class="container position-relative z-1">
    <h2 class="section-title text-center mb-0" id="features-title">Core Features</h2>
    <SectionOrnament />
    <p class="section-kicker text-center mx-auto">Claim land, build a kingdom, manage members and upgrades, strategize with various turrets, mines & structures, form nations and engage in diplomacy, defend your Nexus, and fight for territory.</p>
    <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 row-cols-lg-3 g-3 feature-band">
      <article class="col">
        <div class="feature surface-panel surface-lift text-center h-100 rounded-3">
          <i class="feature-icon fa-solid fa-border-none" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <h3 class="mb-0">Land claiming</h3>
          <p>Let players claim chunks, view nearby territory with /k map, and protect their base with clear borders and configurable claiming rules.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="col">
        <div class="feature surface-panel surface-lift text-center h-100 rounded-3">
          <i class="feature-icon fa-solid fa-landmark-flag" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <h3 class="mb-0">Kingdom management</h3>
          <p>Use the Nexus to manage members, custom ranks & permissions, upgrades, resource points, taxes, shields, turrets, structures, and kingdom settings.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="col">
        <div class="feature surface-panel surface-lift text-center h-100 rounded-3">
          <i class="feature-icon fa-solid fa-skull-crossbones" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <h3 class="mb-0">Wars & Invasions</h3>
          <p>Attack enemy kingdoms through invasion mechanics with champions, defenses, surrendering, ransacking, and server-configurable war rules.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="col">
        <div class="feature surface-panel surface-lift text-center h-100 rounded-3">
          <i class="feature-icon fa-solid fa-shield-halved" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <h3 class="mb-0">Turrets & Structures</h3>
          <p>Defend land with turrets and mines. Use structures like powercells, extractors, warp pads, regulators and outposts to power defenses and increase productivity.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="col">
        <div class="feature surface-panel surface-lift text-center h-100 rounded-3">
          <i class="feature-icon fa-solid fa-scale-balanced" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <h3 class="mb-0">Nations & Diplomacy</h3>
          <p>Create alliances, manage relations, build nations, use relation attributes, and shape how kingdoms interact with each other across the server.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="col">
        <div class="feature surface-panel surface-lift text-center h-100 rounded-3">
          <i class="feature-icon fa-solid fa-gears" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <h3 class="mb-0">Highly configurable</h3>
          <p>Configure messages and chat formatting, customize GUIs, mechanics, upgrades, powerups, economy features and other parts of the plugin to fit your server just right.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
